Package model.implementations.components.manifests

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssetManifest
    An Asset is identified by an asset GUID (incarnation).
    AtomManifest
    Manifest describing an Atom.
    BasicManifest
    The BasicManifest defines the base implementation for all other manifests.
    CompoundManifest
    A compound is an immutable collection of (references to) atoms or other compounds (contents).
    ManifestConstants
    This class contains some useful constants for constructing manifests.
    ManifestFactory
    This factory is used to create manifests for atoms, compounds and assets.
    SignedManifest
    Abstract class for all manifests that support signatures.
